\"http://www.omniveo.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/demo-rm1-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"Ver Tours Virtuales\" title=\"Ver Tours Virtuales\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-2589\" /></a>Los hotspots pueden situarse en cualquier parte de las imágenes para desplazarse de habitación o simplemente para ofrecer puntos de información (como merchandising, productos en venta). Esta es la forma que puede impresionar a sus clientes utilizando la última tecnología de imagen, en cualquier punto del mundo a cualquier hora del día.\r\n\r\nLos tours virtuales pueden incorporarse fácilmente en su website sin la necesidad de bajarse ningún plug-in. Del mismo modo pueden ir acompañados de un mapa orientativo y se pueden diseñar bajo su propio estilo añadiendo los logotipos y pantallas de espera deseados. Si por el contrario no dispone de website, le ofrecemos los cualitativos servicios de diseño y hosting de webs de nuestros cuidadosamente seleccionados partners de Reino Unido (PickaWeb) y España (Merkaweb).\r\n\r\n[portgallery type=\"slider\"]<!--:--><!--:en--><span class=\"dropcap\">O</span>mniVeo is an innovative company that produces 360° Interactive Virtual Reality panoramic images. These can be used to enhance websites with Virtual Tours or send as an Electronic Brochure on CD or via email.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.omniveo.com/portfolio-tag/virtualtour/?lang=en\"><img src=\"http://www.omniveo.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/demo-jh1-300x153.jpg\" alt=\"See Virtual Tours\" title=\"See Virtual Tours\" width=\"300\" height=\"153\" class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-2590\" /></a>The panoramic images give the viewers a sense of standing in the actual environment without having to travel to it. The environment could be your shop, hotel or house, but could even be a city, attraction park or golf course. In the virtual image your customers can pan left and right as well as from top to bottom with a full 360°. By jumping from image to image, guided by a map and/or \'hotspots\', they perceive the feeling of walking through your environment.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.omniveo.com/portfolio-tag/virtualtour/?lang=en\"><img src=\"http://www.omniveo.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/demo-rm1-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"See Virtual Tours\" title=\"See Virtual Tours\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-2589\" /></a>The hotspots can be positioned anywhere in the images to jump to other images or to jump to thematic information (goods you are selling). This is the way to impress your customers using the latest imaging technology, anywhere in the world and anytime in the day.\r\n\r\nThe virtual tours can be easily incorporated in your own website without the need for downloading a plug-in. They can be accompanied by a map and can be designed in your own style with your own logos and wait-screens. But you can also decide to have your website designed and/or hosted by our carefully selected partner in the United Kingdom (PickaWeb) and Spain (MerkaWeb).\r\n\r\n[portgallery type=\"slider\"]<!--:-->','<!--:en-->Virtual Tours<!--:--><!--:es-->Tours Virtuales<!--:-->','','publish','closed','open','','virtual-tours','','','2012-11-16 18:02:57','2012-11-16 18:02:57','',0,'http://www.omniveo.com/wp/?page_id=1869',0,'page','',0),(1855,1,'2012-04-23 10:52:55','2012-04-23 10:52:55','<!--:en--><h4><span style=\"color: #64738c;\">Bienvenido a Omniveo!</span></h4>\r\n<h5>Creamos un mundo virtual con <span style=\"color: #5AC8E5;\">fotos panorámicas 360&deg;,</span>&nbsp;<h1><span style=\"color: #5AC8E5;\">Tours Virtuales</span> y <span style=\"color: #5AC8E5;\">multimedia 3D</span></h1>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #ec6d4a;\">27.01.2027</span> massa</h1>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #64738c;\">Pellentesque laoreet porta purus mollis eget</span></h6>\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #64738c;\">arcu vel orci elementum hendrerit dolor sit.</span></h6><!--:-->','<!--:en-->Intro<!--:--><!--:es-->Int