panoramic images give the viewers a sense of standing in the actual environment without having to travel to it. The environment could be your shop, hotel or house, but could even be a city, attraction park or golf course. In the virtual image your customers can pan left and right as well as from top to bottom with a full 360°. By jumping from image to image, guided by a map and/or \'hotspots\', they perceive the feeling of walking through your environment.\r\n\r\nThe hotspots can be positioned anywhere in the images to jump to other images or to jump to thematic information (goods you are selling). This is the way to impress your customers using the latest imaging technology, anywhere in the world and anytime in the day.\r\n\r\nThe virtual tours can be easily incorporated in your own website without the need for downloading a plug-in. They can be accompanied by a map and can be designed in your own style with your own logos and wait-screens. But you can also decide to have your website designed and/or hosted by our carefully selected partner in the United Kingdom (PickaWeb) and Spain (MerkaWeb).<!--:--><!--:es-->Las imágenes panorámicas permiten al espectador tener un sentido de permanencia física en el entorno real sin tener que desplazarse un ápice. Dicho entorno puede ser su establecimiento, hotel o casa, pero puede ser incluso una ciudad, parque de atracciones o un campo de golf.\r\nEn una imagen virtual sus clientes pueden tomar una panorámica tanto de izquierda a derecha como de arriba abajo con una total visualización de 360 grados.\r\nO lo que es más, podrá saltar de una imagen a otra, siempre con la ayuda de un mapa-guía o mediante uso de hotspots emulando perfectamente un paseo en un entorno real.\r\n\r\nLos hotspots pueden situarse en cualquier parte de las imágenes para desplazarse de habitación o simplemente para ofrecer puntos de información (como merchandising, productos en venta).\r\n\r\nEsta es la forma que puede impresionar a sus clientes utilizando la última tecnología de imagen, en cualquier punto del mundo a cualquier hora del día.\r\nLos tours virtuales pueden incorporarse fácilmente en su website sin la necesidad de bajarse ningún plug-in. Del mismo modo pueden ir acompañados de un mapa orientativo y se pueden diseñar bajo su propio estilo añadiendo los logotipos y pantallas de espera deseados. Si por el contrario no dispone de website, le ofrecemos los cualitativos servicios de diseño y hosting de webs de nuestros cuidadosamente seleccionados partners de Reino Unido (PickaWeb) y España (Merkaweb).<!--:-->','<!--:en-->Virtual Tours<!--:--><!--:es-->Tours Virtuales<!--:-->','','inherit','open','open','','1869-revision-2','','','2012-04-23 18:07:28','2012-04-23 18:07:28','',1869,'http://www.omniveo.com/wp/?p=1871',0,'revision','',0),(1872,1,'2012-04-23 18:13:23','2012-04-23 18:13:23','<!--:en-->OmniVeo is an innovative company that produces 360° Interactive Virtual Reality panoramic images. These can be used to enhance websites with Virtual Tours or send as an Electronic Brochure on CD or via email.\r\n\r\nThe panoramic images give the viewers a sense of standing in the actual environment without having to travel to it. The environment could be your shop, hotel or house, but could even be a city, attraction park or golf course. In the virtual image your customers can pan left and right as well as from top to bottom with a full 360°. By jumping from image to image, guided by a map and/or \'hotspots\', they perceive the feeling of walking through your environment.\r\n\r\nThe hotspots can be positioned anywhere in the images to jump to other images or to jump to thematic information (goods you are selling). This is the way to impress your customers using the latest imaging technology, anywhere in the world and anytime in the day.\r\n\r\nThe virtual tours can be easily incorporated in your own website without the need for downloading a plug-in. They can be accompanied by a map and can be designed in your own s